Package org.openwms.core.uaa.admin

Contains implementation of the Administration feature.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RoleService
    A RoleService provides business functionality regarding the handling with Roles.
    SecurityService
    A SecurityService defines functionality to handle SecurityObjects, especially Grants.
    UserService
    An UserService offers functionality according to the handling with Users.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GrantController
    A GrantController.
    RoleController
    A RoleController.
    UserController
    An UserController represents a RESTful access to Users.
